<tr id="L372"><td><a href="#L372">372</a></td><td>CRUSHER:  And you're saying there's nothing you can do about it?</td></tr>

<tr id="L373"><td><a href="#L373">373</a></td><td>PICARD:  It isn't that simple. I barely know who she is, and who she is changes the moment the next man comes into the room.  And I find myself hoping that the next man won't come in. But, of course, he does, and in a few hours, the ceremony will begin and she will mate with a man who cares more about trade agreements than he cares about her. And I can't help thinking how she will be with him. How she will change to accommodate him.</td></tr>

